{"lemma":"طِفْلٌ","slug":"طِفْلٌ","root":"ط.ف.ل","root_slug":"ط-ف-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-ف-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"طِفْل","root":"طفل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":4},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26832"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B7%D9%90%D9%81%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"child (a minor)","examples":[{"text":"الطِّفْلُ فِي الْمَغَارَة وَأُمُّهُ مَرْيَم وَجْهَانِ يَبْكِيَانِ\nيَبْكِيَانِ لِأَجْلِ مَنْ تَشَرَّدُوا\nلِأَجْلِ أَطْفَالٍ بِلَا مَنَازِل","english":"The child and his mother Maryam in the cave, two faces crying.\nCrying for those made homeless,\nFor children without houses."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"children (a minor)","tags":["collective"],"examples":[{"text":"وَنُقِرُّ فِي الْأَرْحَامِ مَا نَشَاءُ إِلَى أَجَلٍ مُسَمًّى ثُمَّ نُخْرِجُكُمْ طِفْلًا ثُمَّ لِتَبْلُغُوا أَشُدَّكُمْ","english":"˹Then˺ We settle whatever ˹embryo˺ We will in the womb for an appointed term, then bring you forth as infants, so that ye may reach your prime. Some of you ˹may˺ die ˹young˺, while others are left to reach the most feeble stage of life so that they may know nothing after having known much."},{"text":"أَوِ الطِّفْلِ الَّذِينَ لَمْ يَظْهَرُوا عَلَى عَوْرَاتِ النِّسَاءِ","english":"or children who are still unaware of women’s nakedness."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/tˤifl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26832","headword_ar":"طِفْلٌ","root":"Tfl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A young one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"youngling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K, *) of anything, (K,) [or] of a human being and of a beast: (Msb:) or (K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a new-born child,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young infant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a young one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of any wild animal: (S, O, K:) or it is applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a child until he discriminates;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA;) after which he is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabiY~","text_ar":"صَبِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; thus some say, (Msb,) [and] thus says El-Munáwee: (TA:) or, accord. to Az, (Msb, TA,) on the authority of AHeyth, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a child from the time of his birth"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until he attains to puberty:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, TA:) fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TifolapN","text_ar":"طِفْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Zj, Mgh, Msb, TA:) and pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTofaAlN","text_ar":"اَطْفَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Zj, S, O, Msb, TA:) but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TifolN","text_ar":"طِفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also used as fem., (Zj, Mgh, O, Msb, TA,) and dual, (Zj, TA,) and pl., (Zj, S, O, Msb, TA,) occurring as pl. in the Kur xxiv. 31, (S, O, Msb,) and [xxii. 5 and] xl. 69: (Zj, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TifoyalN","text_ar":"طِفْيَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TifolN","text_ar":"طِفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;) used in this sense by a rájiz; but accord. to some, by poetic license, for the dim. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TufayolN","text_ar":"طُفَيْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Any part or portion"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything, whether a substance or an accident: (K, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTofaAlN","text_ar":"اَطْفَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": whence they say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tifolu Alham~i","text_ar":"طِفْلُ الهَمِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHub~i","text_ar":"الحُبِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The portion of anxiety"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of love"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A falling spark"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siqoT","text_ar":"سِقْط"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqaT","text_ar":"سَقَط"},{"kind":"text","text":"]) of fire: (M, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a live coal:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fire when just struck;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TifolapN","text_ar":"طِفْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, TA: [but this latter is the n. un.:]) and the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTofaAlN","text_ar":"اَطْفَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taTaAyarato A^aTofaAlu","text_ar":"تَطَايَرَتْ اَطْفَالُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAri","text_ar":"النَّارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sparks of the fire"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became scattered"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Small clouds:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in a verse of Aboo-Dhu-eyb. (TA.) ―         -b5-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An object of want:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small object of want."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yasoEaY fiY A^aTofaAli AlHawaAy^iji","text_ar":"هُوَ يَسْعَى فِى اَطْفَالِ الحَوَايِجِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. [(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He labours in the accomplishment of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small objects of want."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.)       -A2-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first part thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b2-  And (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sun when near to the setting."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","Msb","S","O","TA","Mgh","Zj","M","A"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}